duties_responsibilities.duty: Coordinate with the project's design team from concept to completion
Supervise the design intent and oversee the design team
Conduct client presentations and ensure the production of complete, accurate, and well-coordinated documents
Handle complex projects and manage multiple projects concurrently
Establish and maintain effective client relationships for the duration of the project
Make design and documentation decisions using discretion and good judgment
Manage designers to foster individual productivity and professional development
Assist in project proposals and marketing efforts

education_certification.credential: Graduate of an accredited Interior Design program or related design program with a Bachelor's level degree
